name: Kyle Rittenhouse Weeping
description: During the murder trial of Kyle Rittenhouse, the defendant made crying gestures but apparently shed no actual tears, nor showed any other remorse for his actions. In 2020, Kyle Rittenhouse shot three men with an assault rifle, killing two of them and wounding the third, during a protest against police brutality in Kenosha, Wisconsin. One of the deceased, Joseph Rosenbaum, was shot four times at point blank range.
